        Minimum length = 1  
        Maximum length = 31 
    .PARAMETER fqdnspoofedip 
        Spoofed IP address range that can be used by client for FQDN based split tunneling.  
        Minimum length = 1 
    .PARAMETER netmask 
        The netmask for the spoofed ip address.  
        Minimum length = 1 
